longBusinessSummary: Okuma Corporation manufactures and sells machine tools, NC controllers, FA products, and servo motors in Japan, the United States, rest of the Americas, Europe, China, and the Asia Pacific. It offers lathes, multitasking machines, machining centers, grinders, and IT/CNC products; and automation products and after sales services. The company was founded in 1898 and is headquartered in Niwa, Japan.
